.TH CALCU 1 "March 2026" "0.1.0" "Calcu Manual"
.SH NAME
calcu \- a minimal calculator
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B calcu
[\fB\-i\fR] [\fIexpression\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B calcu
is a minimal installable calculator with both a graphical user interface and a command-line interface. By default, running it without arguments starts the GUI.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-i, \-\-interactive
Start the interactive terminal calculator.
.SH EXAMPLES
.B calcu 2 + 2
.br
.B calcu "math.sin(math.pi / 2)"
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.local/state/calcu/calcu.log
Error log file for calcu
.SH AUTHOR
Leo
